    <div class="content">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>At Newport Family and Sports Chiropractic, we are dedicated to transforming lives through exceptional chiropractic care. Our practice is built on a foundation of compassion, integrity, and a commitment to empowering our community.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To provide top quality chiropractic care to our community by creating a friendly, welcoming environment where patients feel supported and empowered. Through personalized care and a commitment to chiropractic principles, we help individuals live pain-free, healthier lives and reach their fullest potential.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>To inspire others to prioritize their health and well-being through the power of chiropractic care one adjustment at a time.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <p>Our core values guide every interaction, treatment, and decision within our practice:</p>
        <div class="values">
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Compassion</h3>
                <p>We listen with empathy and treat every individual with kindness and respect. Compassion is the foundation of meaningful patient-centered care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Integrity</h3>
                <p>We uphold honesty, transparency, and ethical behavior in all aspects of our practice. Patients can trust that their health and well-being are our top priorities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Excellence</h3>
                <p>We strive for the highest standards in chiropractic care, continuously improving our skills and knowledge to provide the most effective, evidence-informed treatments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Empowerment</h3>
                <p>We educate and support our patients to take charge of their health journey. We believe informed patients make better health decisions and experience greater long-term wellness.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Community</h3>
                <p>We are committed to fostering a welcoming, inclusive environment where everyone feels valued. We aim to positively impact not only individual lives but also the broader community through holistic health practices.</p>
            </div>
